{"body": "I didn't get this feature. In this case:\n\n```ruby\nclass FixTLMigration < ActiveRecord::Migration\n  def change\n    revert do\n      create_table(:horses) do |t|\n        t.text :content\n        t.datetime :remind_at\n      end\n    end\n    create_table(:apples) do |t|\n      t.string :variety\n    end\n  end\nend\n```\n\nIn the migration `up` the tables `horse` and `apples` will be create. In the migration `down`, do will the two table removed?", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/7746565", "created_at": "2012-08-15T02:35:48Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/7280#issuecomment-7746565", "updated_at": "2012-08-15T02:35:48Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 7280, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/rafaelfranca", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F2c7b84fa30f0cea96a90729afe2970a0.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/received_events", "gravatar_id": "0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "rafaelfranca", "type": "User", "id": 47848, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237fd99bd3543c15100bb71"}, "id": 7746565, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/7280"}
